Detective Azuma is a Dirty-Harry style rogue cop who often uses violence and 
unethical methods to get results. While investigating a series of drug-related 
homicides, Azuma discovers that his friend and colleague, Iwaki, is supplying 
drugs from within the police force. After Iwaki is murdered and Azuma's sister 
is kidnapped, he breaks all the rules to dish out his particular form of justice.


